          LinkBuds Fit

          Always-on with a comfortable fit

          Truly Wireless Noise Canceling Earbuds

          Designed for comfort

          Small, light, and smart, with a secure and comfortable fiteven when exercisingthanks to the newly developed Air Fitting Supporters and earbud tips to keep you connected throughout your day.

          Stay connected with ambient sound

          LinkBuds Fit combines excellent noise canceling with an improved Ambient Sound Mode. When activated, it automatically adjusts to your environment, reducing excess noise while keeping you safe and aware of your surroundings.

          Advanced Noise Canceling

          Equipped with dual noise sensors and the Auto Noise Canceling Optimizer, the LinkBuds Fit earbuds filter exterior sound and adjusts to your surroundings for optimal audio performance.

          Immersive audio and call clarity

          Its easier than ever to stay connected to the people and content you love. Enjoy your favorite music without distractions and exceptional call quality, even in noisy environments.

              Comfortable and secure

              LinkBuds Fit combines a shape that perfectly matches the human ear with an ergonomic design for a more stable fit.

              Multipoint Connection

              For total convenience, these Bluetooth earbuds can be paired with two Bluetooth devices at the same time.

              A stylish case design

              We've updated the classic LinkBuds case design, with a lid that's now easy to open and close in any orientation and an open posture that exudes class.

              IPX4 splash and sweat-proof

              With an IPX4 water resistance rating, splashes and sweat wont stop these Sony earbuds, so you can keep on moving to the music.

              Works with LinkBuds Speaker

              Auto Switch seamlessly swaps playback between LinkBuds earbuds and LinkBuds Speaker (sold separately) automatically.

              Listen all day

              Up to 5.5 hours of battery life and up to 21 hours with charging case. Quick charging gives up to 60 minutes of playback with a 5 minute charge.

              Whats in the box

              Open up the packaging of your Linkbuds Fit and you'll find 4 sizes of earbud tips, air fitting supporters, and a USB-C charging case.

              Intuitive controls

              Control the volume and access your music without touching your phone, and assign customized functions to each earbud in the Sound Connect app.
